            "label": "Description",
            "type": "String",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>Your touch afflicts the target with goblin pox, an irritating allergenic rash. The target must attempt a Fortitude save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Goblin Pox</strong> (disease); <strong>Level</strong> 1. Goblins and goblin dogs are immune.</p>\n<p><strong>Stage</strong> <strong>1</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened} 1 (1 round);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> Sickened 1 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed} 1 (1 round);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> Sickened 1 and the creature can't reduce its Sickened value below 1 (1 day)</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is Sickened 1.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is afflicted with goblin pox at stage 1.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is afflicted with goblin pox at stage 2.</p>"
